    "created_at": "2016-02-05T23:18:46Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-02-05T23:18:46Z",
    "body": "Are there any standard ways to _remove_ flags in a build system ala `CFLAGS`? It's not something I've ever seen before.\n\nIt would be easy to make [all these settings](https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/blob/master/mk/cfg/i686-apple-darwin.mk) overridable wherever they aren't, though I'm not sure that is powerful enough.\n",
