    "updated_at": "2016-02-06T08:34:43Z",
    "body": "FWIW, _all_ user supplied *FLAGS & VARIABLES should be honoured, this includes CC, {C,L,PP,XX}FLAGS, LIBS et al. That is, they should be the last variable on any assignment line, and never appended to.\n",
